title: Local Black Stars coach Konadu tries to keep a lid on hype on teen strike star Joel Fameyeh
text:
FIFA 2010 Sports News | 23 October 2015 12:10 CET Local Black Stars coach Konadu tries to keep a lid on hype on teen strike star Joel Fameyeh - www.ghanasoccernet.com Joel Fameyeh 
Local Black Stars coach Maxwell Konadu admits he faces a battle to manage the expectations growing around Asokwa Deportivo striker Joel Fameyeh. 
The 18-year-old hogged the headlines over the weekend after he hits a brace for the Local Black Stars in their 2-1 win over Cote D'voire in the 2016 CHAN qualifiers. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
